headline: Nvidia And These AI Plays Lead 5 Stocks Near Buy Points
summary: Nvidia, touted as the "de facto AI infrastructure company" in a Friday note, and Coherent, another AI data center play, lead this weekend's watch list of five stocks near buy points.  In addition to NVDA and COHR, construction-equipment supplier United Rentals has data center exposure.  Nvidia has a 99 IBD Composite Rating out of a possible 99, according to IBD Stock Checkup.
